                    <img alt="" src="~/Content/Images/melisturgut.jpg" style="max-width: 168px; max-height: 234px; min-width: 168px; min-height: 234px; " class=" img-circle">
                    <p><strong>Melis Turgut</strong></p>
                    <p><small>Şef</small></p>
